# SvelteKit Routes

Follow `sveltekit-best-practices` (`.cursor/skills/sveltekit-best-practices/SKILL.md`).

- `+page.server.ts` for server-only load (secrets); `+page.ts` for shared load
- Throw `error()` / `redirect()` from `@sveltejs/kit`
- Feature state in Rune classes (`src/lib/state/`), not in components
- URL is source of truth for navigation state (`?city=`)
